Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:06.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:37.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?\NSome lowly commoners just won.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:41.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.25,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:47.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, he's so ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.50,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You finally awake, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:56.80,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,So my magic is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to spill everything \Nto the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.87,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,including who you guys are \Nand what your motives are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.18,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:08.39,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the end has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.08,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic: Ice Burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:22.62,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:26.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think life is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:02:00.66,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}What Happened on a Certain \NDay in the Castle Town
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:04.90,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:12.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:18.56,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:24.20,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:30.44,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:35.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:40.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:46.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:49.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.50,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.80,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you guys went through hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.75,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he sound so happy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.18,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Someone even died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:21.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain, I don't think \Nthis is a laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:25.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Being depressed isn't going to \Nbring Old Man Seihi back. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.41,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! It's just as you say, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:32.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Seihi liked to see \Neveryone happy and energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. You guys should be laughing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.17,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.04,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.81,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Lady Noe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:58.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to\NOld Man Seihi really is a shame,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but you three were able \Nto protect the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:11.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. Great job, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.85,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:23.47,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You moron! You don't even know \Nthe Magic Knights' salute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.76,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.51,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,These fingers symbolize the clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:31.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.10,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:42.36,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vanessa! Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we went to the\NMagic Investigation Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Did you find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.55,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck's behind all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find their hideout and raid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the crap out of \Nthe guy who got away, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.08,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:05.59,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,they investigated the item he left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,but still don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,How useless can they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:19.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop breaking stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:26.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But that pocket watch is pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:31.51,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and from what you said \Nabout how they were acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.78,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,they were all of very high status.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.81,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,So they're royalty or nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who's this little guy? He's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How's it adorable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-It {\i1}is{\i0} adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:50.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You ugly little bird! \NI'll turn you into fried chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you turn him into fried chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two trying to break the building?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.57,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.82,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one breaking everything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:16.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:22.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if the ones behind \Nthis are royalty or nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to let the \NInvestigation Department
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,take care of this, \Nand we'll wait for their report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I've got some good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.11,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:34.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:40.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Your actions have been acknowledged \Nby the Wizard King himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:41.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You've been given a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.44,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.91,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.73,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so excited if you \Ndon't know what they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:04.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Stars are awarded by the Wizard \NKing based on our performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are they good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well... They're like an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Honor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.53,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Asta! Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.55,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's a badge of honor for a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:17.12,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lady here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's a badge of honor for a man and a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.98,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The various Magic Knights squads\N compete to get the most stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:30.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The number of stars indicates \Nhow much work a squad has done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:37.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of, the Golden Dawn is currently \Nat the top with seventy stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seventy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What about us? How many \Ndo the Black Bulls have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose to the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,finally have a nice, even negative thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Negative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally only a hundred \Naway from the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:13.38,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to take forever to catch \Nup and beat them! Damn it, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.99,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:20.20,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Should I really be in this squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.29,main,yami,0000,0000,0000,,One other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your pay for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's money! There's at \Nleast 200,000 yuls here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:35.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:40.68,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Captain! I'm going to eat \Nlots of yummy things with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:46.59,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain! How much would \Nit take for you to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.92,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.69,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:56.12,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about buying new clothes \Nfor my goddess, my little sister, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will look best on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:01.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:06.16,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's gonna be a day off, \Nso don't let it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:09.05,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on tons of dates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.16,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.36,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:22.10,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,We should all go out somewhere and \Nhave fun. What do you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You could buy at least ten years' \Nworth of tatoes with this money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Tatoes? What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:35.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes from Hage Village that taste \Nbland and have a questionable texture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.15,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:42.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't! Sister Lily can \Nmake anything taste good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:42.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:46.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The woman I'm going to marry someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:51.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't sisters women of the cloth? \NI don't think they can get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:56.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-It'll work out somehow! \NI'll go beyond all limitations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.37,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats on your first payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.21,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:10.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to send some money \Nback to the church in Hage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:14.11,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea, Asta! \NThat's the manly thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:17.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Do you send money back, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.63,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.62,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Only after I've increased it a hundredfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.87,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.96,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,A man's gotta take risks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,By "man," you must mean "moron."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:36.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Sending some money back is \Nfine, but don't send it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.65,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Use a little bit for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I use it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:47.49,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go shopping in the \Ncastle town tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.89,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.83,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Lily, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.81,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:09.29,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All of the kind senior squad members \Nare taking good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.08,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, stand right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.68,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.58,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.00,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.34,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:28.89,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.67,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.60,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.27,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:41.20,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I did really well on my first mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:45.56,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and received a star from the Wizard King \Nfor my excellent performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:51.30,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I might be able to \Nbecome the Wizard King by next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:56.66,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become the Wizard King and make \Nthis a world where everyone can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:12:00.71,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll come for you, so please marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:05.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, I just had my first payday, \Nso I'm sending you the money."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:10.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is an awesome letter, \Nif I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sister Lily \Nwill be moved to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.22,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been to the castle town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:44.05,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess royals and nobles wouldn't \Nreally have reason to go very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:49.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I just passed through when I went to \Ntake the Magic Knights Entrance Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:52.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a lot of fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop touching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it! Do you want me to fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:02.57,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about \Nhim for some reason. Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:14.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom is split between the \NNoble Realm, where royalty and nobility live,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23016_226_Saussy_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Saussy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23132_228_Spade_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Spade Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23016_221_Forsaken_Realm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Forsaken Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23016_227_Rayaka_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Rayaka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23016_225_Heart__Kingdom_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Heart\N Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23016_222_Common_Realm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Common Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23016_223_Noble_Realm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Noble Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:19.83,sign_23016_224_Diamond__Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond\N Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Common Realm, where the commoners live,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and the Forsaken Realm, \Nwhere the peasants live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:23.92,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Castle Town of Kikka, \Nwhere Asta and Yuno took
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:27.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights Entrance Exam, \Nis in the Common Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's still amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's very lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:49.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can bring Sister Lily and the \Nkids from the church here someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.07,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:01.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, my goddess, I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:06.42,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your smiling face as soon \Nas possible. I can't contain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.37,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.70,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.48,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.95,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.43,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,The ultra ultimate super \Nlarge serving of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.83,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to eat all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.08,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the nummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:44.76,main,charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.09,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting heartburn just watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.91,main,finral,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some time, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Want to have some tea with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.10,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:02.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You can bring your kids along. \NI know a great place—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.95,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think they're my kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.73,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,They're my brother and sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.19,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry home so we can open the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.08,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any time to mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:14.75,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I love tough young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.04,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, want to have some fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too far ahead, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you two want to buy anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:33.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There are just so many things, \NI don't know what to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:39.68,main,Townsperson A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, those robes... They're Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:45.26,main,Townsperson B,0000,0000,0000,,That mark... Ugh, it's the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:48.57,main,Townsperson A,0000,0000,0000,,That's the lush witch Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:52.39,main,Townsperson C,0000,0000,0000,,Are the cute girl next to her and \Nthe little kid also Black Bulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.24,main,Townsperson B,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably best to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They're starting to get a bit restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:03.37,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Magic Knights being \Nin town helps deter crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:07.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, some fine \Ngentlemen might approach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:14.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I've bought some healing herbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.42,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,as well as some shique ointment, \Nwhich acts as a poison antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.89,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I bought what I needed, so why don't \Nwe go somewhere a bit more quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.84,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I know just the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.18,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:36.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this just some alley?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.73,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:05.29,sign_24543_291_Black_Market,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1008,1040)}Black Market
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.97,top,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Black Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.83,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Market?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:13.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit dangerous, but they have \Nsome very effective magical items.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:17.21,main,Shopkeep,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vanessa. I got some good stuff in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'll take a look later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't seem too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Royals and nobles won't set foot \Nin here because of their prejudices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:38.51,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't control your \Nmagical powers yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,They have items that can help you \Ncontrol your magical powers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:51.11,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If you can find an item that's a good\N fit for you, and adjust your powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.73,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,you might be able to control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Control my powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.86,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take a look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's really lively over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You two are a bit too \Nyoung to go in there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:11.54,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Amateurs shouldn't spend too much time \Nin there, or it could ruin their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.96,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make my paycheck\N grow a hundredfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:21.36,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.60,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I lost again! Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.60,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:35.61,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! That old lady's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:41.66,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I really shouldn't be wasting time \Nhere, anyway. I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:46.56,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the job's to catch a purse-snatcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.63,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even a job for a Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.67,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.59,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,But the captain would get \Nreal scary if I refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:02.43,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that?\NI'll slice you in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:08.26,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! I finally managed \Nto join the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:11.13,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,but it's the Green Praying Mantises.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:15.02,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a praying mantis. A frickin' bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:18.26,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,All I do every day is run errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:21.69,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,When I finally got an actual mission, \NI got used as bait and almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:24.49,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm constipated and my hair's thinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.68,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:30.45,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:35.50,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What about this? You could probably \Nuse this to stabilize your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so cheesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.92,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.21,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:57.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have been walking there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:02.99,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Well, well,\N what brings you two down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:09.56,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Market is no place \Nfor you lovely ladies. Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.44,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:16.29,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,As an elite member of the Magic Knights, \NI shall guide you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:18.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, you insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.00,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:25.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I found something really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:28.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't actually buy that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:29.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.57,main,Doll,0000,0000,0000,,We are hoomans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.74,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.59,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, you're Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.50,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sekke! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been, Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.53,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Bah-ha! No, wait, Sekke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I took the Entrance Exam with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.79,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're a member of the \NGreen Praying Mantises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:02.74,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,He's with two beautiful girls?! Wait, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.68,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,They're both members of \Nthe Black Bulls, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:10.48,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you bastard! \NYou're making me jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:16.97,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's all your fault that \NI ended up in the Green Praying Mantises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:20.81,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! You infuriating bah-hastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.33,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:37.08,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,My winnings! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:55.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:22:01.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:09.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:16.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:19.62,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:31.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:37.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:45.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:51.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:56.80,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
