Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:18.93,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,1)}Sekke's Bah-Ha Seminar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:18.32,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sekke's Bah-Ha Seminar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:20.43,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:22.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:22.68,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:23.94,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:25.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:29.44,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you have yet to learn \Nthe ways of the bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:30.94,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The ways of the bah-ha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:38.29,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! This is my chance \Nto make a name for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:42.32,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch the thief and \Nget praise from the Wizard King, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:46.36,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 12:\N"The Wizard King Saw."
